    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! \ud83c\udf1f I\u2019m selling my absolute pride and joy, and let me tell you, she\u2019s a total stunner! This car is in truly incredible condition\u2014honestly, it looks and feels like it just rolled off the showroom floor. I\u2019ve babied it since day one, kept it tucked away in the garage, and kept it sparkling clean. It drives like an absolute dream and is just waiting for someone new to love it as much as I have. You really have to see this beauty in person to believe how perfect it is! Feel free to reach out with any questions\u2014I'd love to chat!",
