    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_9_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_9",
      "description": "Presenting a collector-grade 2004 BMW M3 (E46) featuring the iconic S54 3.2L inline-six power plant with individual throttle bodies. This example exhibits exceptional mechanical provenance, including a documented VANOS overhaul and proactive rear subframe reinforcement. The Getrag 6-speed manual transmission provides crisp engagement, paired with a factory limited-slip differential for optimal torque distribution. Suspension geometry remains factory-spec with zero bushing deflection, ensuring the sharp turn-in and lateral stability these chassis are renowned for. A true turnkey specimen for the discerning purist.",
