    {
      "id": "sybil_10_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_10",
      "description": "This is a true showroom-quality time capsule that has been fastidiously maintained in a climate-controlled garage. The exterior retains its deep, mirror-like factory luster with a professional ceramic coating and zero rock chips or swirl marks. Inside, the cabin is indistinguishable from new; the premium leather bolsters show no signs of entry wear, the dashboard remains supple without a hint of UV exposure, and it still carries that distinct new-car aroma. Mechanically, the vehicle is flawless, featuring a fully documented service history with every interval performed at the dealership. All electronics, from the infotainment to the heated seat elements, function perfectly. It sits on a fresh set of matching high-performance tires and includes both original keys, all manuals, and the window sticker. This is the cleanest example on the market, ready for a discerning collector or an enthusiast who accepts nothing less than perfection.",
      "price": 43500.0,
